 And it sets in motion a huge number of biological cascades

19:04.600 --> 19:07.080
 within every cell and organ of your body,

19:07.080 --> 19:09.640
 from your liver to your gut, to your heart, to your brain.

19:09.640 --> 19:11.800
 It really sets things down the right path.

