 It's very important that that pulse of cortisol

19:38.320 --> 19:40.140
 arrive early in the day.

19:41.300 --> 19:42.440
 I want to emphasize this again.

19:42.440 --> 19:44.680
 It's very important that that pulse of cortisol

19:44.680 --> 19:46.360
 arrive early in the day.

